These are Puzzles for 4x2 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-8-1::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: 7up, cola
There 2 different types of food: plum, cherry
The people have 2 different hobbies: reading, woodworking
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: animation, crime
1. the person watching animation movies is not to the right of the person eating cherry##8
2. the person eating cherry is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is reading##5
3. the person drinking 7up is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |
| Beverage      | cola     | 7up      |
| Food          | cherry | plum    |
| Hobby         | woodworking   | reading |
| Movie-Genre   | animation  | crime      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-8-2::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: lemonade, coffee
The people have 2 different hobbies: drawing, photography
The people have 2 different jobs:  videographer, bartender
The people use 2 different means of transport: ship, bus
1. the person drinking coffee is on the far right##1
2. the person who's hobby is drawing is somewhere to the left of the videographer##5
3. the bartender is not to the right of the videographer##8
4. the person driving the ship is not the person who's hobby is photography##6

.:: Answer ::.
|             |         1          |      2      |
| Beverage    | lemonade        | coffee    |
| Hobby       | drawing         | photography |
| Job         | bartender | videographer   |
| Transport   | ship               | bus  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-8-3::.
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: crime, scientific
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: hip-hop, gospel
There are 2 different nationalities: thai, malaysian
2 different pets are kept: rabbit, hamster
1. the thai is in an odd position##4
2. the malaysian is not to the right of the owner of the hamster##8
3. the fan of hip-hop is somewhere to the left of the person watching scientific movies##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |
| Movie-Genre   | crime       | scientific |
| Music-Genre   | hip-hop       | gospel    |
| Nationality   | thai | malaysian |
| Pet           | rabbit        | hamster   |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-8-4::.
