The people have 2 different jobs:  entrepreneur, fisherman
There are 2 different nationalities: italian, thai
The people use 2 different means of transport: quad-bike, van
1. the italian is somewhere to the right of the fisherman##5
2. the person who's hobby is skydiving is not to the left of the person driving the van##8
3. the person driving the van is on the left of the person who's hobby is skydiving##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2     |
| Hobby         | gardening | skydiving  |
| Job           | fisherman  | entrepreneur |
| Nationality   | thai | italian   |
| Transport     | van   | quad-bike |

