There are 2 different nationalities: polish, french
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: biathlon, skiing
The people use 2 different means of transport: van, scooter
1. the person driving the scooter is on the left of the person driving the van##1
2. the polish is on the left of the person who's sport is biathlon##1
