2. the owner of the pony is on the left or right of the person drinking juice##3
3. the person watching time-travel movies is on the right of the person watching crime movies##1
4. the person eating avocado is on the right of the owner of the pony##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |
| Beverage      | iced-tea      | juice  |
| Food          | pepper   | avocado    |
| Movie-Genre   | crime | time-travel |
| Pet           | pony       | bird     |

